; The Unit test runtime — extracted as its own sub-library (fennec-hunt.unit) so:
; 1. The ppx can generate `Fennec_hunt_unit.test_loc` without creating a cycle when
;    fennec-hunt self-hosts its own inline tests.
; 2. It stays reusable independently (the runtime has no ppx / browser / http deps).
; 3. The main fennec-hunt library re-exports it as Fennec_hunt.Unit.

(library
 (name fennec_hunt_unit)
 (public_name fennec-hunt.unit)
 (libraries unix)
 (modules fennec_hunt_unit))
